ğŸŒŸ About the Project

NaluXrp is a high-performance, real-time analytics platform built as an SPA that runs entirely client-side.
It connects live to XRPL nodes via WebSocket, aggregates ledger events, visualizes validator performance, and provides modules for:

Ledger and transaction monitoring

XRPL validators & UNL deep-dive

Token exploration and metadata

AMM pool analytics

NFT scanning

Whale activity

System health metrics

Network visualization

Customizable themes

Full mobile-responsive UI

The app is designed to feel like a professional trading terminal meets blockchain explorer, but smoother, lighter, and fully front-end based.

