ğŸ“¥ Installation
1. Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/YourRepo/NaluXrp.git
cd NaluXrp

2. Open locally

No backend required.

Just open index.html in a browser, or run a lightweight server:

npx serve


or:

python3 -m http.server 5500

3. Configure API Notes

If using localhost, some Ripple endpoints require a CORS proxy.
The app is structured to support:

thingproxy.freeboard.io

allorigins.win

Custom proxies

You can configure them in:

js/validators.js
js/explorer.js
js/analytics.js

