ğŸ”— XRPL Data Sources
WebSocket

wss://s1.ripple.com

wss://s.altnet.rippletest.net:51233 (Testnet)

REST

https://data.ripple.com/v2/network/validators

https://api.xrpldata.com/ (optional)

https://livenet.xrpl.org (explorer queries)

ğŸ”’ Security

This is a frontend-only analytics tool:

No seeds, keys, or signing operations occur in the browser.

No user wallet data is stored or transmitted.

Always warn users never to paste private keys into any unverified interface.

ğŸ¤ Contributing

We welcome contributions!

Developer Guidelines

Follow the modular JS structure.

Maintain navbar.js â†’ mobile-first behavior.

Keep CSS scoped to module files.

Use descriptive commits:

feat(validators): add agreement anomaly detection
fix(navbar): resolve iOS scroll-lock bug

Pull Request Rules

Format with Prettier or standard JS style

No console spam

Include screenshots for UI changes

